defaultAbout Impetus – The Private Equity Foundation
defaultImpetus – The Private Equity Foundation (Impetus – PEF) accelerates the growth of innovative charities and 
defaultsocial 
defaultenterprises helping disadvantaged
default children and young people to get the start in life they deserve. 
