defaultImpetus-PEF
default was formed in June
default 2013 following the merger of I
defaultmpetus Trust and the Private Equity Foundation. The new organisation has backed a total of 48 organisations, including 26 in its active portfolio. In 2011/12 the Impetus – PEF port
defaultfolio helped 566,000 disadvantaged people.
defaultWe also research and campaign on the topics of educational attainment and work readiness, to influence public deb
