defaultrces to where they might have most impact in these areas. 
defaultAbout our port
defaultfolio
defaultWithin our 26 strong active portfolio, 11 organisations work with young people at risk of educational failure, or with those who have already ‘failed’ in mainstream education. Between them, they work all over the UK, and with boys and girls from dive
defaultrse backgrounds, including white working class
default young people
