defaultdraw young people in, and then 
defaultlet 
defaultthem
default succeed when they are used to failing. 
defaultThese lessons deserve to 
defaultbe reflected on by schools, as well as by services such as CAMHS.
default CAMHS was described by one respondent, with extensive experience as ‘an intimidating service’ for young people. 
