defaultCEO of a charity working with young offendersdefaultMany respondents expressed a strong des
defaultire for a system which genuinely had academ
defaultic aspirations for all children, as well as high-quality vocational pathways and options. 
defaultBut most were wary that a resurgence in talk of ‘improved vocational options’ would actually result in low-quality, second-
